message: Hello. My name is Chris. Thank you for reaching out to VoyageQuest. How can I assist you with your travel plans today?
Hi, I booked a flight with you recently, but I haven't received my e-ticket. I think it's a missing e-ticket issue. Can you help?
I'd be happy to assist with that! Let's just run through security. Can you confirm your name? Can you also confirm your address? Finally, please confirm your reference number.
Sure, my name is John Smith, my address is 124 Main Street, and my account number is 123456.

Thank you, John. That's all correct! I can see your booking for your upcoming flight to New York. Your e-ticket should have been sent to your registered email address. Have you checked your spam or junk folder?
Yes, I checked everywhere, but I still can't find it.
No problem, John. I’ll go ahead and resend your e-ticket to your registered email address right now. Would you like me to send it to an alternative email as well, just in case?
Yes, please send it to john.smith.work@email.com as well.
Got it! I’ve just resent your e-ticket to both your registered and alternative email addresses. Please check and confirm if you’ve received it.
Yes, I’ve received it now. Thanks so much for your help!
You're very welcome, John! Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that’s all for now. Thanks again, Chris.
You're very welcome! Have a great trip, and feel free to reach out if you need any assistance in the future. Goodbye!
